WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:02.800
But truly, I'm frightened.

00:02.800 --> 00:07.400
Not of the ghost, I've lived with Margaux's memory my whole life.

00:07.400 --> 00:11.400
I'm frightened of what happens when the wrecking ball comes.

00:11.400 --> 00:15.400
Where does an old actress go when her stage is gone?

